{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":110,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":"char_zhuo_san_niang","text":"那……那又如何？","tone":"疑问","chapter":60,"line_start":2,"line_end":2},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"那时正义之师，便将全军覆没。","tone":"陈述","chapter":60,"line_start":4,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":"char_zhuo_san_niang","text":"那时我等好歹也得想个法子，将毒神……","tone":"焦急","chapter":60,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"非当事之人，谁也不准插手，这话你莫非忘了？","tone":"厉声","chapter":60,"line_start":8,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":"char_zhuo_san_niang","text":"难道你……你竟眼见他们死？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":60,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"我行事素来公正，既不许别人为'五福联盟'帮拳，便也不许有人相助大旗门。若有谁敢妄自出手，须得先过了我卓三娘这一关。","tone":"认真","chapter":60,"line_start":14,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":"char_zhuo_san_niang","text":"你明知大旗门要遭毒手，才说出这样的话来；你明明有所偏袒，还说什么行事公正。你……你……你简直……","tone":"激动","chapter":60,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"好大胆的女子，在三娘面前说话，也敢如此无礼，莫非你只道三娘没有手段封住你的嘴么？","tone":"厉声","chapter":60,"line_start":22,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"事已至此，你还哭什么？且瞧瞧那边吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":60,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":null,"text":"呀！不好。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":60,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_yun_yi","speaker_name":"云翼","listener":"char_tie_qing_shu","text":"好孩子，再上。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":60,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_tie_qing_shu","speaker_name":"铁青树","listener":"char_yun_yi","text":"是！","tone":"激动","chapter":60,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"看来你对那小伙子倒不错。","tone":"调侃","chapter":60,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":"char_zhuo_san_niang","text":"哼！","tone":"陈述","chapter":60,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_yi_ming","speaker_name":"易明","listener":"char_zhuo_san_niang","text":"风九幽也不是当事人，你也不能让他出手。","tone":"认真","chapter":60,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_san_niang","speaker_name":"卓三娘","listener":"char_yi_ming","text":"你放心，他不会出手的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":60,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_feng_jiu_you","speaker_name":"风九幽","listener":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","text":"抬起头来。","tone":"沉声","chapter":60,"line_start":76,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","speaker_name":"飧毒大师","listener":"char_feng_jiu_you","text":"你……你要怎样？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":60,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_feng_jiu_you","speaker_name":"风九幽","listener":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","text":"望着我。","tone":"沉声","chapter":60,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_feng_jiu_you","speaker_name":"风九幽","listener":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","text":"你上次与我交手，我虽中了你的毒，你却也被我迷住，只是那时你心灵还坚强，中迷又不深，是以还能支持，只不过行事已略为有些疯狂而已，别人虽能瞧出，你自己却丝毫不会觉察。","tone":"柔声","chapter":60,"line_start":88,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_feng_jiu_you","speaker_name":"风九幽","listener":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","text":"但你此刻已被花二娘暗器所伤，你一生善于用毒，却无法解去花二娘暗器之毒……你说是么？","tone":"柔声","chapter":60,"line_start":96,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_feng_jiu_you","speaker_name":"风九幽","listener":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","text":"是以你此刻正全心全意，不让那毒气攻心，是以你防护心灵的意志，便减弱了，你已无法再抵挡我。","tone":"柔声","chapter":60,"line_start":102,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_feng_jiu_you","speaker_name":"风九幽","listener":"char_xiu_du_da_shi","text":"这就是了，你此刻心灵已全都被我控制，你自己再也没有半点主意，你只有听我的话才对，是么？","tone":"柔声","chapter":60,"line_start":108,"line_end":110}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yi_ming","name":"易明","alias":[],"identity":"武林中人","faction":"大旗门","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"大旗门相关人物，关心大旗门安危的年轻女子","personality":{"traits":["刚烈","正义感强","重情重义","冲动","有同情心"],"speech_style":"直率","temperament":"急躁"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_tie_qing_shu","type":"恋人","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"深情关注"},{"target":"char_yi_ting","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"兄妹相依"},{"target":"char_zhuo_san_niang","type":"对手","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"敬畏不满"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[60],"source_refs":[{"chapter":60,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"易明失色道"}]},{"id":"char_zhuo_san_niang","name":"卓三娘","alias":[],"identity":"武林绝顶高手","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"武林绝顶高手，行事看似公正实则暗藏算计","personality":{"traits":["深谋远虑","冷酷","伪善","精明","心狠手辣"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yi_ming","type":"对手","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"压制"},{"target":"char_hua_shuang_shuang","type":"合作者","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"表面和睦"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[60],"source_refs":[{"chapter":60,"line_start":4,"line_end":4,"text":"卓三娘道"}]},{"id":"char_yi_ting","name":"易挺","alias":[],"identity":"武林中人","faction":"大旗门","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"易明之兄，与易明一同在场","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","忍耐","护妹","刚毅","沉默"],"speech_style":"稳重","temperament":"内敛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yi_ming","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"兄妹相依"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[60],"source_refs":[{"chapter":60,"line_start":26,"line_end":26,"text":"易挺自也是怒愤填膺"}]},{"id":"char_yun_yi","name":"云翼","alias":[],"identity":"大旗门掌门","faction":"大旗门","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"大旗门掌门，最终与毒神同归于尽","personality":{"traits":["刚烈","侠义","无畏","豪迈","悲壮"],"speech_style":"豪迈","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yun_jiu_xiao","t